{"tid":1091326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"褫奪瓜伊多豁免權 馬杜羅擬刑事檢控","createTime":"2019-04-04T05:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T05:53:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc19b5ee0e9fafe1c47ce7c8b69902235a49d587","tid":1091326,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190404/20648450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F20648450&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvCiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=3b69dc6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F20648450&h=eb117e5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190404/20648450</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n褫奪瓜伊多豁免權 馬杜羅擬刑事檢控<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190404/large/a1903a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190404%2Flarge%2Fa1903a.gif&h=775e7e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n委內瑞拉民眾爬上擋在委國與哥倫比亞邊境的一個貨櫃上。路透社<br />\n<br />\n受委內瑞拉馬杜羅政府掌控的制憲大會前日宣佈，褫奪自行宣誓成為臨時總統的反對派領袖瓜伊多享有的國會議員豁免權，疑為刑事檢控他鋪路。瓜伊多就警告，「若這個政權膽敢綁架我、發動叛變，我們就會強硬回應」。<br />\n<br />\n瓜伊多作為全國代表大會議長，擁有國會豁免權，當局要檢控他有一定難度。但制憲大會主席卡奉韋略（Diosdado Cabello）前日就宣佈，議員一致同意授權最高法院對瓜伊多進行審訊。制憲大會內的議員全屬馬杜羅忠心派。<br />\n<br />\n瓜伊多2月違反最高法院年初頒下的離境禁令，到訪拉丁美洲多國爭取支持。前日法院重申他仍然受制於禁令。瓜伊多亦正面臨多項調查，總檢察長辦公室已開始調查他，在1月牽涉的連串「暴行事件」；審計長阿莫羅索指控他，外訪資金來歷不明；但當局暫未曾拘捕或起訴他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n若遭「綁架」將強硬回應<br />\n<br />\n瓜伊多前日回應指，得悉制憲大會的投票結果，「但我們不會改變前進的路徑」。他也於Twitter上指，若馬杜羅「綁架」他，將招來強硬回應，「我們跟各國領袖溝通過，篡位者不會想測試國際社會的決心」。<br />\n<br />\n德新社/路透社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n雲頂9.8億買涉一馬案遊艇<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n汶萊新法 同性戀、通姦者可判石刑"},{"pid":"1f60c300637db87b022ea30192f8bf0bf429b3b9","tid":1091326,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:10:19.000Z","msg":"幾時DQ佢唔比佢做議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e764b8d80cc0ac851d336694e3e59a44d0f838","tid":1091326,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:12:46.000Z","msg":"美國出兵打柒馬杜羅啦，我好想睇支爆呀！"},{"pid":"330d729ad2a04f610ccbd177e2eab3007cc9fc8e","tid":1091326,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:18:20.000Z","msg":"打返場代理戰先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410341e0f7a8e9eb200e637e9eb9402bb7b36cdb","tid":1091326,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"美國到宜家都唔出手<br />\n唔通真係驚咗中俄反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87749ab010feff4295ad061c8c86368ad225ddaf","tid":1091326,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"兒燈仔日盼夜盼的焦土。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}